<div class="space-y-6">
<h2 class="font-h2 text-h2 text-on-surface">Warm, Professional, and Welcoming</h2>
<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-primary"></div>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                        At TP Hair Design, we believe that luxury should be felt the moment you step through our doors. Our Blair Athol sanctuary is designed for those who value professional expertise combined with a serene, pampering environment.
                    </p>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                        Our team of master stylists is dedicated to the art of hair. From precision cutting to bespoke color transformations, we take the time to understand your unique lifestyle and aesthetic goals, ensuring a result that is both stunning and sustainable.
                    </p>
<div class="flex items-center space-x-4 pt-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">verified</span>
<span class="font-label-caps text-on-surface-variant uppercase">Certified Master Colorists</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
